<paragraph blockId="25.[132,775,1449,1574]" pageId="25" pageNumber="536">
ETYMOLOGY. — From the Latin 
<emphasis box="[448,510,1523,1547]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="536">tessella</emphasis>
